data.description: Generous Price Improvement!  Pool, Solar, and Golf are a Few of the Amenities Offered at 9625 Warwick, Located in the Desirable Community of Mission Lakes....This Single Story Three Bedroom Home Offers Open Living Room with Fireplace and Dining Room with Easy Access to Kitchen  Equipped with Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Counters, Possible Walk-Through Pantry, Eating Area with View of Front of Property....There are Two Primary Bedrooms One with Custom Bathroom with Walk In Shower, Built In Vanity, the Other with Views of Pool and Entry to Outside Enclosed Patio Space....A Bonus Room/Den with Fireplace can Easily be Converted to a Fourth Bedroom...The Backyard Pool and Spa Add a Peaceful Retreat Area... Leased Solar, New Air Condition, New Water Heater, Crown Molding, Laundry Room with Sink and MEMBERSHIP TO COUNTRY CLUB GOLF Compliment the Balance of this Fine Property...[Great News! The Living Room, and Bedrooms Can be Your Blank Canvas to Add Your Own Personal Touch for Flooring!]
